==JB_SUMMER_REDUX_V1==
--By Puni--

Inspired by Summer, I attempted to make a "nicer" version. 

Its very basic, little detail. I went for a slick look with not to much going on.

Map Features

    * 40 Spawns
    * Summer Styled Cell, Spawn & Medic Area
    * Climbing Area
    * Playable Football Pitch with Regular & Penalty Shootout Mode
    * Bulldog Arena
    * Large Swimming Pool
    * Bunnyhop Area
    * Last Request Stable
    * 2 Secrets

--

It was a beta for my communitys servers, but its here for others to see. Being a beta dont expect it to be bug free. Please report any bugs back asap.

==========
